{"tid":2202024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藏人呼籲藏港連結　「中國政府就好像是病毒、細菌——只用一種藥物是無法殺菌的」","createTime":"2020-09-14T09:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T12:35:09.000Z","uid":261647,"like":164,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"3396d7b31250a1116c27c120fe929f9b10a46770","tid":2202024,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159444197202448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10159444197202448&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=701c0674\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159444197202448</a><br />\n<br />\n作為受中國霸權打壓的藏人，阿旺認為歐盟也有責任抵抗。他獨自從巴黎踩單車到瑞士日內瓦，全程近600公里。<br />\n<br />\n阿旺發起網上聯署，希望網民可以支持他的單車行，並一同要求中共將自由及基本人權還給西藏、香港及維吾爾族人，他說：「中國政府就好像是病毒、細菌&mdash;&mdash;只用一種藥物是無法殺菌的，要有破壞細菌外膜的藥，要有防止細菌繁殖的藥；再有一些外力的幫助，像是中美貿易戰、中印邊境問題，中國政府才會越來越弱。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mn6qcoq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMn6qcoq.png&h=373d935d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a61052c78085d47f3137f275351b002d9ec3f20","tid":2202024,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b61e68617ac4b20469aaac6bf31e00b20ac5711","tid":2202024,"uid":11291,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"支那共產黨呢個病毒一定要連根拔"},{"pid":"cf102ad0f38e2d8101ef8462b9e88068a6b49663","tid":2202024,"uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:16:11.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定要連結到 點講都係一齊受迫害"},{"pid":"cbbe3abe6adff9dddfb9ab2dae4a9dd12198c2c8","tid":2202024,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3396d7b31250a1116c27c120fe929f9b10a46770","tid":2202024,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159444197202448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10159444197202448&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=701c0674\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159444197202448</a><br />\n<br />\n作為受中國霸權打壓的藏人，阿旺認為歐盟也有責任抵抗。他獨自從巴黎踩單車到瑞士日內瓦，全程近600公里。<br />\n<br />\n阿旺發起網上聯署，希望網民可以支持他的單車行，並一同要求中共將自由及基本人權還給西藏、香港及維吾爾族人，他說：「中國政府就好像是病毒、細菌&mdash;&mdash;只用一種藥物是無法殺菌的，要有破壞細菌外膜的藥，要有防止細菌繁殖的藥；再有一些外力的幫助，像是中美貿易戰、中印邊境問題，中國政府才會越來越弱。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mn6qcoq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMn6qcoq.png&h=373d935d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">====================<br />\n</span><span class=\"medium\">大家要注意資安，尤其是被咬過嘅手足，電話可能已經被入侵。<span class=\"red\">港共可以用stingray<strong>大規模監控</strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，偷取IMSI，可以識別您</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重資安<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><span class=\"gold\">和你塞admin</span></strong>同埋<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong><span class=\"x-small\">; 行蹤洩漏嘅原因: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2200973/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2200973/</a> </span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsancti